# iosApp — Phase 2

This directory will hold the SwiftUI presentation layer (iOS 26 Liquid Glass) once Phase 1
compiles green. The Xcode project will be created here in Phase 2 and will link against
the `ThapsusShared.framework` produced by `:shared:linkPodReleaseFrameworkIosArm64`
(or via the `embedAndSignAppleFrameworkForXcode` task wired through SKIE).
